invasion of Kuwait in 1990 and release all Kuwaiti and non-Kuwaiti
prisoners of war still detained in Iraqi jails.
</P>
<P>
The Kuwaiti official said Kuwait's participation in the meeting
emanates from its belief in the positive role played by the
movement in supporting international causes and its effective role
in the United Nations.
</P>
<P>
The meeting would review world economic and political
developments and is expected to release a final statement
explaining the movement's policies regarding international
problems, he said. 
