process has failed to secure any progress, it is due to Israel's
wish to dominate the Arab region, to retain the occupied Arab
territories and set up more Jewish settlements on them.
</P>
<P>
He reaffirmed his country's adherence to the peace process in
accordance with the Madrid conference, the relevant U.N.
resolutions, as well as the land-for-peace principle and the
agreements reached in the past years. 
