China and Egypt, two giants of ancient culture, have shared the
same or similar viewpoints on many issues and have constantly
shown solidarity and sympathy for each other in international
affairs.
</P>
<P>
The Egyptian leader, who is also chairman of the ruling
National Democratic Party, expressed the hope that the
friendly cooperation between the two countries and their ruling
parties will be further strengthened.
