<HEADLINE> Xinhua World News Summary at 0800 GMT April 6 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON -- The United States will keep a significant
military presence in Asia even if there will be a peaceful
reunification of the Korean peninsula, U.S. Defense Secretary
William Cohen said on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
COLOMBO -- With the ongoing drought reducing the country's
