<BODY>
<HEADLINE> U.S. Team Leads Netherlands 2-1 in Davis Cup Tie </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 5 (Xinhua) -- The United States led The
Netherlands 2-1 after losing its doubles match in the Davis Cup
quarter-final tie in Newport Beach, California on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Paul Haarhuis and Jacco Eltingh of the Netherlands defeated
Rick Leach and Jonathan Stark of the United States 6-4, 6-4, 3-6,
6-3. 
